40KRB5_LIB_FUNCTION krb5_error_code KRB5_LIB_CALL
41krb5_decode_EncTicketPart (krb5_context context,
42 const void *data,
43 size_t length,
44 EncTicketPart *t,
45 size_t *len)
46 KRB5_DEPRECATED_FUNCTION("Use X instead")
47{
48 return decode_EncTicketPart(data, length, t, len);
49}
